<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/778627-does-this-specific-edition-of-the-bachman">Does this specific edition of the &quot;Bachman Books&quot;
ISBN-13: 978-0450392498 has the novella Rage in it?

It&#39;s almost costing me a fortune to buy this (since it&#39;s said to be out of print) but the seller cannot tell me exactly whether it has rage in it or not because it&#39;s coming from a hub which is not located near his office/residence. I am willing to spend such amount on this book if and only if it has &quot;Rage&quot; in it.</a>
</div>
