<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1402492-of-all-the-stories-in-the-bachman-books">Of all the stories in The Bachman Books The Long Walk will haunt me most. A wonderful homage to Philip K Dick - it gives you &#39;They Shoot Horses Don&#39;t They with Hunger Games. However - my question is this - Rage is in the 1986 print that I got from the charity shop, I assume it does not appear in later versions because if tells a school shooting from the shooter&#39;s perspective - is that right?</a>
